description: Creates a new Power BI Workspace Collection with the specified properties. A Power BI Workspace Collection contains one or more workspaces, and can be used to provision keys that provide API access to those workspaces.

subscription_id.description: Gets subscription credentials which uniquely identify a Microsoft Azure subscription. The subscription ID forms part of the URI for every service call.

workspace_collection_name.description: Power BI Embedded Workspace Collection name
